quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  7,164,"Jantii -an Nulaa…óo-, tuma nde ha…óayno…óaa jamaa jeyanoo…óo e ma…ď…ďe gaayi e pankarere, na reentinabe duum, jamaa goo wi'ani …ďen : "Ko hon…óum waajanto…óon yim…ďe, Allaahu ko halkoowo …ďe aduna ko …ďe faggitori kon geddi, maa O letoya …ďe √Ďalnde Darngal lepte sattu…óe?" Waajotoo…ďe …ďen wi'i : "Ko men waajoranta …ďe, ko ittangol Alla nganto ko O yamiri men yamirgol mo∆ī∆īere ha…óa Ňči√Īere hara O nanngitiraali men tertagol …óum, e belajo'o, …ďe nafitora waaju ngun, …ďe …ďooroo e geddi"."
  7,165,"Nde waajanoo…ďe …ďen …óuurnii e ko …ďe waajaa kon, Men da…óndi …ďen ha…óaynoo…ďe e bone on lepte, Men nanngiri …ďen too√Īir…ďe jaggitugol yunngude ka aseweere lepte sa…ótu…óe sabu yaltugol ma…ď…ďe e …óoftaare Alla ha…ď…ďitoo e geddi."
  7,166,"Nde …ďe yawtirnoo keeri Alla …óin townitaare, …ďe salii waajitagol, Men wi'ani : "Onon …ďee yedduu…ďe, laatee baa…ói jaasinaa…ói ; …ďe wonti baa…ói. ∆Āe wontiri no min yi…óiri , tawde fiyaaku amen Men wi'anta huunde nde si Men haajani, ko laato : nde laatoo"."
  7,167,"Janto -an Nulaa…óo-, nde Alla anndinoo wonnde ma O Nulu e …ďee Alyahuudaa…ďe on hoynoowo …ďe ka nguurndam aduna haa √Ďalnde Darngal. Pellet, Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo-, ko yaccii…óo leptugol yeddoowo Mo, toode Himo yaccina leptugol ontigi gila aduna, pellet kadi, ko O haforoowo junuubi tuuboo…ďe e jeyaa…ďe makko …ďen, Hinnotoo…óo …ďe."
  7,168,"Men senndiri …ďe ka leydi Men wa…óti …ďe feddeeji. Hino e ma…ď…ďe : hino ema…ď…ďe mo∆ī∆īu…ďe daranii…ďe haqqeeji Alla …óin e haqqeeji jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, hino e ma…ď…ďe kadi ra…ď…ďindinii…ďe, wo…ó…ďe e ma…ď…ďe fantini e geddi. Men jarribori …ďe neweende e sa…óteende, jortagol nde …ďe tertotoo ko …ďe woni e mun."
  7,169,"Bom…ďe lontii …ďe, …ďe roni Tawreetaare nden maw…ďe ma…ď…ďe, hi…ďe jannga nde kono …ďe gollirtaa, …ďe ∆īettira ngeenaari dakammehoy aduna fii waylugol Deftere nden Alla, √Īaawira go…ó…óum goo, …ďe yelanoo ko'e-ma…ď…ďe nde Alla haforanta …ďe junuubi ma…ď…ďe. Si dakammehoy aduna arii e ma…ď…ďe …ďe ja…ďa …óum. E Alla ∆īettidaali e ma…ď…ďe ahadi wonnde …ďe wowlataa e Alla si wanaa goonga?! ∆Āe saloraali gollirde Deftere nden fii majjere, ko e anndal ma…ď…ďe tigiri, tawde …ďe janngii nden e gollirii. Awa ko junuubi ma…ď…ďe …óin …ďuri tii…óude, ko laakara kadi e neemaaji mun duumii…ói …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …ďen huloo…ďe Alla e diini dakammehoy aduna lannay-koy. E …ďee kan haqqiltaa ko Alla marani kon huloo…ďe Mo …ďen laakara?!"
  7,170,"∆Āen jogitotoo…ďe Deftere nden, …ďe gollira nde, …ďe √Īii…ďinira julde nden reenagol e waqtuuji mayre e sartiiji mayre e wa…ó…óii…ói mayre e sunnaaji mayre, pellet, Alla yo…ďoy …ďe njo…ďdi golle ma…ď…ďe …óen, Alla wanaa yeeboowo njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe golle."